- Use service accounts securely, preferably through environment variables
- Implement proper error handling when interacting with Firebase services
- Use transactions for operations that require atomicity
- Optimize database queries to minimize read/write operations
- Implement proper security rules and validate data on the server-side
- Use V2 functions and Auth with custome cliams. 